<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0,maximum-scale=1.0,user-scalable=no">
<title>👨‍👩‍👧‍👦 家庭健康自查手册 v0.6.2</title>
<style>
:root{--bg:#faf9f6;--card:#fff;--primary:#2d7a5e;--primary-light:#e8f5f0;--primary-dark:#1e5a42;--accent:#e8a84a;--accent-light:#fef6e8;--warn:#e74c3c;--warn-light:#fdecea;--text:#2c2c2c;--text-light:#666;--border:#e0ddd8;--radius:16px;--shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.08)}
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
body{font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"PingFang SC","Microsoft YaHei",sans-serif;background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);line-height:1.7;padding-bottom:80px}
.header{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--primary),var(--primary-dark));color:#fff;padding:28px 20px 36px;text-align:center;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.header::before{content:"";position:absolute;bottom:-30px;left:-20px;width:200px;height:200px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);border-radius:50%}
.header::after{content:"";position:absolute;top:-40px;right:-30px;width:150px;height:150px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border-radius:50%}
.header h1{font-size:21px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:6px;position:relative}
.header p{font-size:14px;opacity:0.85;position:relative}
.header .badge{display:inline-block;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.18);border-radius:20px;padding:4px 14px;font-size:12px;margin-top:10px;position:relative}
.tier-banner{display:flex;gap:8px;padding:12px 16px;background:var(--card);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100}
.tier-btn{flex:1;border:2px solid transparent;background:var(--bg);color:var(--text-light);padding:10px 6px;border-radius:12px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.2s;text-align:center}
.tier-btn .ti{font-size:18px;display:block;margin-bottom:3px}
.tier-btn .ts{font-size:10px;opacity:0.8;display:block}
.tier-btn.active{border-color:var(--primary);background:var(--primary-light);color:var(--primary)}
.tier-btn:active{transform:scale(0.96)}
.tab-bar{display:flex;gap:4px;padding:8px 16px;overflow-x:auto;-webkit-overflow-scrolling:touch;scrollbar-width:none;background:var(--card);position:sticky;top:73px;z-index:99;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.tab-bar::-webkit-scrollbar{display:none}
.tab-btn{flex-shrink:0;border:none;background:var(--bg);color:var(--text-light);padding:6px 12px;border-radius:20px;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.2s;white-space:nowrap}
.tab-btn.active{background:var(--primary);color:#fff}
.tab-btn:active{transform:scale(0.96)}
.section{display:none;padding:18px 16px;max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;animation:fadeIn 0.25s ease}
.section.active{display:block}
@keyframes fadeIn{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(6px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
.sec-header{padding:4px 0 14px}
.sec-header .st{font-size:20px;font-weight:700;color:var(--primary)}
.sec-header .sd{font-size:13px;color:var(--text-light);margin-top:4px}
.tt{display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:20px;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:10px}
.tt.d{background:#e8f4ff;color:#1a73e8}
.tt.m{background:var(--accent-light);color:#a07020}
.tt.y{background:#f3e8ff;color:#7c3aed}
.test-card{background:var(--card);border-radius:var(--radius);margin-bottom:10px;box-shadow:var(--shadow);overflow:hidden;border:2px solid transparent;transition:border-color 0.2s}
.test-card.done{border-color:var(--primary)}
.test-card.fail{border-color:#f0b0a0}
.test-header{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:14px 16px;cursor:pointer;user-select:none;transition:background 0.15s}
.test-header:active{background:var(--primary-light)}
.test-header-left{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px}
.test-icon{font-size:26px;flex-shrink:0}
.test-title{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text)}
.test-sub{font-size:12px;color:var(--text-light);margin-top:2px}
.test-header-right{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}
.test-status{font-size:12px;font-weight:600;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:20px}
.test-status.pass{background:var(--primary-light);color:var(--primary)}
.test-status.fail{background:var(--warn-light);color:var(--warn)}
.test-status.pending{background:var(--bg);color:var(--text-light)}
.test-arrow{font-size:12px;color:var(--text-light);transition:transform 0.2s}
.test-header.open .test-arrow{transform:rotate(180deg)}
.test-body{max-height:0;overflow:hidden;transition:max-height 0.35s ease;padding:0 16px}
.test-body.open{max-height:900px;padding-bottom:16px}
.ml{font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--primary-dark);margin-bottom:8px;margin-top:10px}
.mb{background:var(--bg);border-radius:10px;padding:12px;margin-bottom:4px}
.mb p{font-size:13px;color:var(--text);line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:8px}
.mb p:last-child{margin-bottom:0}
.ct{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:12px}
.ct th{background:var(--primary-light);color:var(--primary-dark);padding:8px 10px;text-align:left;font-weight:600}
.ct td{padding:8px 10px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);vertical-align:top;font-size:13px}
.ct tr:last-child td{border-bottom:none}
.ct td:first-child{font-weight:600}
.cb{display:flex;gap:6px;margin-top:12px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.cbtn{border:2px solid var(--border);background:#fff;border-radius:10px;padding:6px 12px;font-size:12px;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.2s;color:var(--text-light)}
.cbtn.pass{border-color:var(--primary);background:var(--primary-light);color:var(--primary)}
.cbtn.fail{border-color:var(--warn);background:var(--warn-light);color:var(--warn)}
.cbtn:active{transform:scale(0.96)}
.auto-result{display:none;margin-top:14px;border-radius:12px;padding:12px 16px;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;align-items:center;gap:10px}
.auto-result.show{display:flex}
.auto-result.pass{background:var(--primary-light);border:2px solid var(--primary);color:var(--primary)}
.auto-result.fail{background:var(--warn-light);border:2px solid var(--warn);color:var(--warn)}
.auto-result .ar-icon{font-size:20px;flex-shrink:0}
.auto-result .ar-text{flex:1;line-height:1.5}
.auto-result .ar-badge{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:20px;flex-shrink:0}
.auto-result.pass .ar-badge{background:var(--primary);color:#fff}
.auto-result.fail .ar-badge{background:var(--warn);color:#fff}
.sg{display:grid;gap:6px;margin-top:10px}
.so{border:2px solid var(--border);background:#fff;border-radius:10px;padding:8px 4px;font-size:11px;cursor:pointer;text-align:center;transition:all 0.2s;color:var(--text-light);line-height:1.4}
.so.sel{border-color:var(--primary);background:var(--primary-light);color:var(--primary)}
.so.warn{border-color:var(--warn);background:var(--warn-light);color:var(--warn)}
.so .ov{font-size:18px;font-weight:800;display:block}
.so .ol{font-size:10px;font-weight:500}
.so:active{transform:scale(0.95)}
.bc{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(7,1fr);gap:3px;margin:10px 0}
.bi{text-align:center;cursor:pointer;padding:6px 2px;border-radius:8px;border:2px solid transparent;transition:all 0.2s}
.bi.sel{border-color:var(--primary);background:var(--primary-light)}
.bi.sel.warn{border-color:var(--warn);background:var(--warn-light)}
.bi .bt{font-size:20px;display:block}
.bi .bn{font-size:10px;color:var(--text-light);display:block;margin-top:2px}
.bl{font-size:11px;color:var(--text-light);text-align:center;margin-top:6px}
.vi{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;padding:12px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.vi:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.vic{font-size:28px;flex-shrink:0}
.vii{flex:1}
.vin{font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text)}
.vid{font-size:12px;color:var(--text-light);margin-top:2px}
.vinput{width:60px;border:2px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;padding:6px 8px;font-size:14px;text-align:center;outline:none;background:#fff;transition:border-color 0.2s}
.vinput:focus{border-color:var(--primary)}
.vunit{font-size:12px;color:var(--text-light)}
.pw{background:var(--primary-light);border-radius:12px;padding:12px 16px;margin-bottom:4px}
.plabel{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:13px;color:var(--primary-dark);font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px}
.pbar{height:10px;background:rgba(45,122,94,0.2);border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden}
.pfill{height:100%;background:var(--primary);border-radius:10px;transition:width 0.5s ease;width:0%}
.ptip{font-size:12px;color:var(--text-light);margin-top:8px}
.ai{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);font-size:13px}
.ai:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.ai .ic{font-size:18px;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px}
.ai .it{flex:1;line-height:1.5}
.ai .itag{padding:2px 8px;border-radius:20px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;white-space:nowrap;flex-shrink:0}
.ai .itag.fail{background:var(--warn-light);color:var(--warn)}
.ai .itag.pass{background:var(--primary-light);color:var(--primary)}
.card{background:var(--card);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:18px;margin-bottom:14px;box-shadow:var(--shadow)}
.card-title{font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:var(--primary);margin-bottom:12px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}
.form-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:12px}
.form-row label{font-size:14px;color:var(--text);min-width:80px;font-weight:500}
.finput{flex:1;border:2px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:10px 14px;font-size:15px;outline:none;transition:border-color 0.2s;background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);max-width:130px}
.finput:focus{border-color:var(--primary)}
.form-row span{font-size:13px;color:var(--text-light)}
.btn{width:100%;background:var(--primary);color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:12px;padding:14px;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;margin-top:8px;transition:all 0.2s}
.btn:active{transform:scale(0.98);background:var(--primary-dark)}
.rb{background:var(--primary-light);border:2px solid var(--primary);border-radius:12px;padding:16px;margin-top:14px;text-align:center}
.rb .bn{font-size:40px;font-weight:800;color:var(--primary);line-height:1.1}
.rb .bl{font-size:13px;color:var(--primary-dark);margin-top:4px}
.rb .bs{font-size:12px;color:var(--text-light);margin-top:8px;line-height:1.6}
.rt{width:100%;margin-top:14px;border-collapse:collapse}
.rt td{padding:9px 12px;font-size:14px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.rt td:first-child{font-weight:600}
.rt td:last-child{text-align:right;color:var(--primary);font-weight:700}
.alert{background:#fff8e6;border:1.5px solid #f0c060;border-radius:12px;padding:12px 14px;font-size:13px;display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:flex-start;margin-top:12px}
.alert .ae{font-size:18px;flex-shrink:0}
.alert p{color:var(--text);line-height:1.6}
.alert.warnA{background:var(--warn-light);border-color:#e0a0a0}
.fb{background:var(--accent-light);border-left:4px solid var(--accent);border-radius:0 12px 12px 0;padding:12px 16px;margin:12px 0;font-size:13px;line-height:1.7}
.bl2{list-style:none;padding:0}
.bl2 li{padding:8px 0 8px 20px;font-size:14px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);position:relative;line-height:1.6}
.bl2 li:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.bl2 .dot{position:absolute;left:0;top:8px;color:var(--primary);font-weight:700}
.steps{counter-reset:step}
.step{display:flex;gap:12px;margin-bottom:14px}
.step::before{counter-increment:step;content:counter(step);width:26px;height:26px;background:var(--primary);color:#fff;border-radius:50%;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px}
.step-content{flex:1}
.step-title{font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:2px}
.step-desc{font-size:13px;color:var(--text-light);line-height:1.6}
.pg{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:10px}
.pc{background:var(--card);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:16px;text-align:center;box-shadow:var(--shadow)}
.pc .pnum{width:32px;height:32px;background:var(--primary);color:#fff;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:800;font-size:14px;margin:0 auto 8px}
.pc.top .pnum{background:var(--accent)}
.pc .ptitle{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:4px}
.pc .pdesc{font-size:11px;color:var(--text-light)}
.sp{display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:flex-start;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.sp:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.sp .nb{width:22px;height:22px;background:var(--primary);color:#fff;border-radius:50%;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px}
.sp .sc{flex:1;font-size:13px;color:var(--text-light);line-height:1.6}
.sp .sc strong{color:var(--text)}
.faq-item{background:var(--card);border-radius:var(--radius);margin-bottom:10px;box-shadow:var(--shadow);overflow:hidden}
.faq-q{width:100%;background:none;border:none;padding:14px 18px;text-align:left;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);cursor:pointer;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;transition:background 0.15s}
.faq-q:hover{background:var(--primary-light)}
.faq-q .arr{font-size:14px;transition:transform 0.2s;color:var(--text-light)}
.faq-q.open .arr{transform:rotate(180deg)}
.faq-a{max-height:0;overflow:hidden;transition:max-height 0.3s ease}
.faq-a.open{max-height:400px}
.faq-ac{padding:0 18px 14px;font-size:13px;color:var(--text-light);line-height:1.7}
.faq-ac p{margin-bottom:8px}
.faq-ac p:last-child{margin-bottom:0}
.rc{background:var(--card);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:16px;margin-bottom:10px;box-shadow:var(--shadow);border-left:4px solid var(--primary)}
.rc.high{border-left-color:var(--warn)}
.rc .rtitle{font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:4px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px}
.rc .rdesc{font-size:12px;color:var(--text-light);line-height:1.6}
.rc .rtags{display:flex;gap:6px;margin-top:8px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.rtag{padding:2px 8px;border-radius:20px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;background:var(--primary-light);color:var(--primary)}
.rc.high .rtag{background:var(--warn-light);color:var(--warn)}
.info-box{background:#e8f4ff;border-radius:10px;padding:12px 14px;margin:8px 0;font-size:13px;color:#1a4fa0;line-height:1.6}
#scrollTop{position:fixed;bottom:20px;right:20px;width:44px;height:44px;background:var(--primary);color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:50%;font-size:20px;cursor:pointer;box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(45,122,94,0.4);display:none;z-index:200;align-items:center;justify-content:center}
#scrollTop.show{display:flex}
.footer{text-align:center;padding:20px 16px;font-size:12px;color:var(--text-light);max-width:680px;margin:0 auto}
.footer .cr{font-size:11px;color:var(--text-light);margin-top:6px;opacity:0.7}
#splash{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--primary),var(--primary-dark));display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;z-index:9999;animation:sfOut 0.8s ease 2s forwards}
@keyframes sfOut{from{opacity:1}to{opacity:0;visibility:hidden}}
.si{text-align:center;color:#fff}
.si .stitle{font-size:52px;margin-bottom:16px}
.si .stext{font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;opacity:0.9;font-weight:500}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div id="splash"><div class="si"><div class="stitle">👨‍👩‍👧‍👦</div><div class="stext">Made by HopE<br>和他的 AI 助手小爪</div></div></div>
<div class="header" id="top">
  <h1>👨‍👩‍👧‍👦 家庭健康自查手册 v0.6.2</h1>
  <p>祝你早安、午安、晚安</p>
  <div class="badge">🧭 科学自检 · 精准训练 · 全家适用</div>
</div>
<div class="tier-banner" id="tierBanner">
  <button class="tier-btn active" id="tier-daily-btn" onclick="setTier('daily')">
    <span class="ti">🌙</span><span class="tier-name">每日自查</span><span class="ts">睡眠·排泄·情绪</span>
  </button>
  <button class="tier-btn" id="tier-monthly-btn" onclick="setTier('monthly')">
    <span class="ti">📅</span><span class="tier-name">月度自查</span><span class="ts">体重·肌肉·心肺</span>
  </button>
  <button class="tier-btn" id="tier-yearly-btn" onclick="setTier('yearly')">
    <span class="ti">🩺</span><span class="tier-name">年度提醒</span><span class="ts">血液指标·体检</span>
  </button>
</div>
<div class="tab-bar" id="tabBar"></div>
<div class="section active" id="sec-daily-overview">
  <div class="sec-header">
    <div class="st">🌙 每日健康自检</div>
    <div class="sd">每天花 3 分钟，完成当天的基础健康记录</div>
  </div>
  <div class="pw">
    <div class="plabel"><span>今日完成度</span><span id="d-p-text">0 / 4</span></div>
    <div class="pbar"><div class="pfill" id="d-p-fill"></div></div>
    <div class="ptip" id="d-p-tip">开始今天的记录吧 👇</div>
  </div>
  <div class="card" style="background:#f0f7f4;border-left:4px solid var(--primary)">
    <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-light);line-height:1.7">先点击每个模块查看测量方法，测完后点选结果。有手环用设备测，没手环用<strong>零成本方法</strong>，同样准确！</p>
  </div>
  <div class="card" id="d-roadmap" style="display:none">
    <div class="card-title">🗺️ 今日健康小结</div>
    <div id="d-advice"></div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="section" id="sec-daily-sleep">
  <div class="sec-header">
    <div class="st">😴 睡眠质量</div>
    <div class="sd">入睡时长 · 晨起精力 · 白天嗜睡</div>
  </div>
  <div class="test-card" id="test-sleep">
    <div class="test-header" onclick="toggleTest('sleep')">
      <div class="test-header-left"><span class="test-icon">😴</span>
        <div><div class="test-title">睡眠自检</div><div class="test-sub">入睡 · 晨起精力 · 嗜睡</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="test-header-right">
        <span class="test-status" id="status-sleep"></span>
        <span class="test-arrow">▼</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="test-body" id="body-sleep">
      <div class="ml">入睡时长（关灯到睡着）</div>
      <div class="mb">
        <p>上床后多久能睡着？</p>
        <div class="sg" style="grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr">
          <div class="so" onclick="selectScore('sleep-time',this,3,'sleep')"><span class="ov">&lt;15'</span><span class="ol">很快</span></div>
          <div class="so" onclick="selectScore('sleep-time',this,2,'sleep')"><span class="ov">15-30'</span><span class="ol">正常</span></div>
          <div class="so" onclick="selectScore('sleep-time',this,1,'sleep')"><span class="ov">&gt;30'</span><span class="ol">偏慢</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="ml">晨起精力感（1-5分）</div>
      <div class="mb">
        <p>早上醒来，感觉恢复得</p>
        <div class="sg" style="grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr">
          <div class="so" onclick="selectScore('sleep-energy',this,1,'sleep')"><span class="ov">1</span><span class="ol">很累</span></div>
          <div class="so" onclick="selectScore('sleep-energy',this,2,'sleep')"><span class="ov">2</span><span class="ol">有点累</span></div>
          <div class="so" onclick="selectScore('sleep-energy',this,3,'sleep')"><span class="ov">3</span><span class="ol">一般</span></div>
          <div class="so" onclick="selectScore('sleep-energy',this,4,'sleep')"><span class="ov">4</span><span class="ol">较好</span></div>
          <div class="so" onclick="selectScore('sleep-energy',this,5,'sleep')"><span class="ov">5</span><span class="ol">神清气爽</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="ml">白天嗜睡程度</div>
      <div class="mb">
        <p>白天有没有明显困意？（坐着看书/看电视时）</p>
        <div class="sg" style="grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr">
          <div class="so" onclick="selectScore('sleep-drowse',this,0,'sleep')"><span class="ov">从不</span><span class="ol">无困意</span></div>
